            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EHousehold%20salvation%20is%20a%20promise%20stated%20throughout%20the%20Word%20of%20God.%20Paul%20told%20the%20Philippian%20jailer%20that%20if%20he%20gave%20his%20heart%20to%20Jesus%2C%20he%20and%20his%20family%20would%20be%20saved.%20That%20night%20both%20he%20and%20his%20entire%20family%20became%20Christians%20(Acts%2016%3A34).%20At%20that%20moment%2C%20all%20their%20names%20were%20recorded%20in%20the%20Lamb's%20Book%20of%20Life.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAs%20the%20children%20of%20Israel%20waited%20for%20judgment%20to%20fall%20upon%20their%20nation%2C%20they%20were%20instructed%20to%20offer%20a%20lamb%20for%20a%20household%20(Exodus%2012%3A3).%20We%20should%20never%20stop%20pressing%20this%20claim%20of%20the%20Word%20of%20God%20for%20our%20families%20to%20be%20saved%20from%20the%20wrath%20to%20come.%20%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20must%20daily%20bring%20our%20families%20and%20relatives%20before%20the%20Father.%20Noah%20entered%20the%20ark%20with%20his%20entire%20family.%20Job%20prayed%20continually%20for%20his%20children%2C%20in%20case%20one%20of%20them%20had%20done%20something%20to%20offend%20God.%20It%20pleases%20the%20Lord%20when%20we%20remind%20Him%20of%20our%20kindred%20relationship%20to%20our%20families%20and%20stand%20against%20Satan's%20attempts%20to%20totally%20defeat%20them.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPlace%20the%20blood%20of%20Jesus%20daily%20over%20the%20doorpost%20of%20your%20household.%20Claim%20today%20that%20all%20your%20household%20will%20join%20you%20in%20heaven%20and%20will%20bring%20you%20joy%20here%20on%20earth%20as%20well!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
